soccer.common

Interface Field_Constants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TOS_Constants

    public interface Field_Constants
    This class must be the only place for keeping all soccer field hard-coded constants; they all are final. Using locally defined public static constants in other classes is still allowed, yet not recommended.
    Author:
    vkyrylov (2010)
